1. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper proposes a low-complexity detection algorithm for MIMO systems, which is a common topic in information theory.
2. cs.SI (Signal Processing) - The paper deals with signal constellations and detection algorithms, which are core topics in signal processing.
3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - MIMO systems are often used in wireless communication networks, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture.
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new constraint test and a predict-and-change strategy, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - MIMO systems are also used in multimedia applications such as video streaming and image transmission, which falls under the domain of multimedia.
